Tatter D'Malion<br>
Rent-A-Bard <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uredspinebladeslinge.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Redspine Bladeslinge</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Protector of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 512<br> <font color=#CC9900>(1/24/01 4:12:46 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/yellowspine/Redspine_1.bmp WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Discussion on Vox rotation....</span><hr size=1> If anyone needs assistance organizing or leading a Vox Raid I am happy to help out.  Thats why I created Jestur, forever -53 cleric.  <br>
